  <acronym>TRMC-004</acronym>
  <official_title>Use of 31P MRS to Assess Brain NAD+ in Healthy Collegiate Athletes and a Comparison of the Effect of Nicotinamide Riboside Supplementation on Brain NAD+ Levels</official_title>
